  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So next to me, the same evening or the following evening, in the evening, I whispered.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was this girl, Renia Silwerschtz next to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Could you spell her name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Silwer-- Silwer-- S-I-L-W-E-R-Schtz, like you say in German, Schtz-- S-C-H-T-Z, probably something like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was next to me, and she was close to maybe five years older than I was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was a very intelligent girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to her-- then I said the way-- you know, as she was-- we were sort of two, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was like three bunks, and that it was just we were very close together because there were 1,500 girls and 150 girls in-- in a room.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, really, you know, she was right next to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said to her how I felt, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said that I am, you know, like come to a stage when you say, I'm not going to take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was all-- I was going along since it happened with my [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was going along told whatever I was to do, yes?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But suddenly I thought, no whatever I-- that was it, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I felt it's just not enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's just not enough that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we started, and this encouraged her, and her response was terrific because she read what I read, and she knew what I was talking about because she was that much older and her response was such.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it meant that during the day, we went to pieces, you know, whatever allowed us, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were some in bits and pieces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were on this work, and we were, let's say whatever I did in that factory had to be done again in the minutest detail.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
